","msg":"爆咗好耐, 唔明點解block人都設上限<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfc1620268dbdfdd598fb785b75393e2f5f7a4da","tid":668400,"uid":18720,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"688752b83c4b867086fe6c4b064be9642a0ac35f","tid":668400,"uid":7699,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"咁不如直接番高登"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:13:48.000Z","msg":"當時離開高登就係因為五毛橫行同埋啲真/假鍵國撚係度戇鳩當有趣<br />\n<br />\n點知連登因爲ac太易申請，搞到個壇變成一個以放負為榮，以圍爐取暖為樂既竇<br />\n<br />\n我絕對唔係支持盲目負能量，但每日成千上萬個放負區、嘈交post、講啲乜撚買唔到樓/自己冇父幹呢啲垃圾post就長期熱門<br />\n係咁多個post入面想睇啲高質啲既真係大海撈針 好講彩數<br />\n<br />\n所謂「討論」，三句唔埋就屌左老母，死左全家先<br />\n唔理好醜一野label左人地就即刻搶佔高地<br />\n<br />\n好地地一啲資訊性十足既post往往有返百零個reply就會出現戇鳩引戰搞到原本討論緊既人避戰而走<br />\n<br />\n屌那星呢個係大家原本想要既壇咩？"},{"pid":"1bcfa21c09b24885f5bd362e18d19b2bf858d959","tid":668400,"uid":181156,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"block我啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0465e7c603a0754250a3667f03cf8f424e849906","tid":668400,"uid":18720,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"quote":{"pid":"1bcfa21c09b24885f5bd362e18d19b2bf858d959","tid":668400,"uid":181156,"like":1,"dislike":10,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"block我啦撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:30:35.000Z","msg":"你呢啲戇鳩仔正正就係我開post既原因"},{"pid":"c8971aa9b8ce987e519a647cacaf43cc66a011a2","tid":668400,"uid":69679,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"肥絲大隻條撚樣居然無出現無入到來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40a97dd46263b700658af848e35cce48dbeb7ac3","tid":668400,"uid":18720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-17T16:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8055bb729c9f13e482de1b1c4f086